      "content": "That deep, soul-level exhaustion is a heavy burden, and it is okay to feel completely depleted after fighting such a long battle. When everything feels lost, the weight of simply moving forward can seem impossible. Please know that even when you cannot see a reason to fight, reaching out is still a chance to rest within support. Call 988 again; they are there to help carry some of this exhaustion with you right now.",
